---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About - Jay Lee"
  description="About Jay Lee, an enterprise AI adoption and human-agent work systems practitioner based in Seoul."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
        <h1>I work on the adoption layer of AI.</h1>
      </div>
      <p>
        My focus is the space between frontier AI capability and real organizational work: workflow discovery, pilot design,
        eval evidence, governance boundaries, and leader enablement.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid">
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Positioning</h3>
        <p>
          Enterprise AI adoption, workflow transformation, AI Success, human-agent operations, and responsible capability
          capture.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Evidence style</h3>
        <p>
          Public artifacts should be inspectable: code, docs, synthetic examples, eval cases, and clear boundaries about what
          is not being claimed.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Contact</h3>
        <p>
          Seoul-based. Open to AI adoption, AI Success, workflow systems, and public-safe collaboration conversations.
        </p>
        <a href="mailto:2joowon@gmail.com">2joowon@gmail.com</a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
